@page
@model WebApp.Pages.AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About this application.";
}

<style>
    body {
        background-color: #f4f6fb;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .navbar {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2b5876 0%, #4e4376 100%);
    }

    .navbar-brand, .nav-link {
        color: #fff !important;
    }

    .navbar-brand:hover, .nav-link:hover {
        color: #ffd700 !important;
    }


    .alert-info, .alert-danger {
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.05);
        border-left: 5px solid #2b5876;
        background-color: #e3f2fd;
        color: #2b5876;
    }
</style>

<h2 class="mt-3 mb-2">About This Application</h2>

<p>
    <strong>EzLeadGenerator</strong> is a specialized lead intelligence platform built for <strong>talent acquisition professionals</strong> and <strong>recruiters</strong> focused on Data Engineering roles in the Charlotte, NC area.
</p>

<hr />

<h3>What Does This Site Do?</h3>
<p>
    EzLeadGenerator streamlines the process of identifying, analyzing, and acting on Data Engineer job opportunities and company leads. By combining live job market data, AI-powered company analysis, and actionable dashboards, the platform empowers recruiters to quickly discover hiring trends, target the right companies, and connect with potential candidates.
</p>

<hr />

<h3>How the Main Pages Work Together</h3>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Data Engineer</strong>: The primary page, automatically searching for Data Engineer roles in Charlotte, NC. Results are enriched using AI (ChatGPT) to identify company divisions and possible contacts.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Company Leads</strong>: For any company found on the Data Engineer page, view a detailed company profile, including divisions and suggested contacts, to help you target your outreach.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Dashboard</strong>: Visualize the current job market—see which companies are hiring, which agencies are active, and what job titles are trending, all in one place.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Talent Search</strong>: A focused tool for running custom talent searches beyond Data Engineers, giving you flexibility to find candidates for any role.
    </li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h3>Who Is This For?</h3>
<p>
    This application is designed for recruiters, staffing agencies, and business development professionals who want to:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Quickly identify Data Engineer openings in Charlotte, NC and surrounding area</li>
    <li>Analyze hiring companies and discover new business leads</li>
    <li>Find and contact potential candidates or company decision-makers</li>
    <li>Track market trends and hiring activity with real-time dashboards</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<p>
    <em>
        EzLeadGenerator brings together job search, company intelligence, and AI-driven insights—so you can spend less time searching and more time connecting with the right people.
    </em>
</p>

<p>Whether you're prospecting for new clients or filling roles with verified leads, this tool helps unify both sides of the staffing equation.</p>

<p><em>Built with recruiters in mind. Powered by SerpApi. Designed for results.</em></p>
